{"title":"Getaway Like Hemingway","blogimage":{"url":"/assets/images/ndp-marker.jpg"},"url_friendly_name":"getaway-hemingway","date":"2016-06-16","Posted_by":"Admin","short_description":"Ernest arrived in Key West in early 1928. Drawing influences from Havana, Cuba and Key West, Hemingway penned numerous novels during his time in the Keys.","more_content":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12.0pt; line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">Ernest arrived in Key West in&nbsp;early 1928. Drawing influences from Havana, Cuba and Key West, </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.hemingwayhome.com/general/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">Hemingway</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\"> penned </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.hemingwayhome.com/books/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">numerous&nbsp;novels</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\"> during his time in the Keys. He&nbsp;soon built his Spanish Colonial home located at </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.hemingwayhome.com/general/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">907 Whitehead Street</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\"> in 1851, which is now a </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ernest_Hemingway_House\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">national landmark</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\"> that so many people visit while in Key West. During his time in this beautiful home, many say </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.hemingwayhome.com/books/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">Ernest produced his best work</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">: from &ldquo;To Have and Have Not&rdquo;, &ldquo;Green Hills of Africa&rdquo;, and many short stories &ldquo;The Snows of Kilimanjaro&rdquo;, among others.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<h3 class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12.0pt; line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">Present: Celebrating Ernest Hemingway in Key West</span></strong></h3>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12.0pt; line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">We are proud of the rich literary ties Key West has developed over time. It is incredibly important to convey this to our guests and offer them a taste of the Keys to take back with them after their stay. This is why we developed a special package for the guest of our resort. </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://www.themarkerkeywest.com/special/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">The Ernest Hemingway package</span></strong></a></span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">includes a bottle of </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://papaspilar.com/#/papaspilar/landing\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">Papa&rsquo;s Pilar</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\"> rum and tickets to the </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.hemingwayhome.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">Hemingway House</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\"> for a tour of the grounds, complete with some adorable six-toed cats. </span></p>\n<h3 class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12.0pt; line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">Papa&rsquo;s Pilar</span></strong></h3>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12.0pt; line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">Named after Hemingway&rsquo;s beloved sailing vessel (his muse for many a novel),&nbsp; </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://papaspilar.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">Papa&rsquo;s Pilar</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\"> rum which, &ldquo; (brings) together rums from throughout the Caribbean, Florida and Central America into one single pour&rdquo; was a must-include in our Hemingway package. Not only was it inspired by the Man himself, but there will soon be a Papa&rsquo;s Pilar distillery mere blocks from The Marker Resort! </span></p>\n<h3 class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12.0pt; line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">Fishing Charters</span></strong></h3>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12.0pt; line-height: 16.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">To round out a true Hemingway experience, our concierge will be on hand to recommend and book fishing charters to take you out and experience one of Hemingway&rsquo;s favorite pass times. Charters that top our list include </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.bestkeywestfishing.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">Captain Moe&rsquo;s Lucky Fleet</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\"> and </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.timeflysfishing.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">Time Flys Fishing.</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\"> Hitting the high seas with these experienced Captians is sure to garner you a &ldquo;big fish&rdquo; story or two!</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">If you&rsquo;re a Hemingway fan and are looking for special way to celebrate your stay, we encourage you to take advantage of our <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Ernest Hemingway package. </span></strong>While you&rsquo;re exploring the open seas, a walk down the same streets he strolled, or a tour of the famous </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.hemingwayhome.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">Hemingway House</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">, make sure to take some pictures to remember your vacation. If you share them on social with </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/lovethemarker/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">#LoveTheMarker</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">, we may share your picture on our </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/themarkerresort/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">Instagram</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue';\">!&nbsp;</span></p>"}